# ─── Copyrighted paper content ───────────────────────────────────────
*.pdf
*_text.txt
hake_reread.txt

# ─── Images (paper screenshots / pasted images) ──────────────────────
*.png
*.jpg
*.jpeg
*.gif
*.webp
*.bmp

# ─── Personal research notes at repo root ────────────────────────────
# Exclude all top-level .md except README
/*.md
!/README.md

# Research outputs produced by the skills (keep locally, don't share)
/seminar-report-*.md
/slide-draft-*.md
*.base
/wikilink.md

# ─── Research content under note/ (keep only Templates) ──────────────
/note/*
!/note/Templates/
/note/.obsidian/

# ─── Raw paper sources ───────────────────────────────────────────────
/raw/*
!/raw/README.md

# ─── Wiki research content (keep only schema templates) ──────────────
/wiki/concepts/
/wiki/entities/
/wiki/sources/
/wiki/synthesis/
/wiki/log.md
/wiki/review-history.md
/wiki/pending-review.md
/wiki/integration-progress.md
/wiki/wiki/

# ─── Personal Claude Code / Claudian state (any depth) ───────────────
**/.claude/sessions/
**/.claude/settings.json
**/.claudian/

# ─── Obsidian personal state and plugin binaries (any depth) ─────────
**/.obsidian/workspace.json
**/.obsidian/workspace-mobile.json
**/.obsidian/workspace.json.bak
**/.obsidian/plugins/

# ─── OS / OneDrive artifacts ─────────────────────────────────────────
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
~$*
*.tmp
.DS_Store
